{
  "stem": "3804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In other words, he didn't want to stay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A very difficult life in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My-- my brother was very young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He start work and never studied because he have to work to, you know, have some money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So our life was not easy coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my brother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yachiel",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jacob-- and Jacob.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jacob died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I told you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Yachiel also died, but about seven years ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am the only one who stayed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, to-- to live in a Jewish village with the Polish and all this, and I-- when I came back to visit my home and all this, I really felt again the smell of Polish people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm ?] [? not ?] the same for sharing all this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the atmosphere of unwanted-- And even now when I came, I felt it now with the Polish because they've been very afraid when I came to see my home that I'm going to take back the home.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You should know that 200 people, 200 Jews have been killed after the Holocaust when they came back to take their houses, been killed by the Polish when they want to take back their-- their property.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they didn't try anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So let's say, the atmosphere of unwanted, I felt it very much now, even now.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I felt it then as a boy that you are being afraid when you walk to home with a small lamp, you know, because [INAUDIBLE] with the candle.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've always been afraid of the-- of the Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody will attack you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I look like a Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- when I was big-- bigger, I look more than a-- than English or-- the English looked.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
